trans-unit.source: Provides an implementation of the OLE DB <see langword="IRowsetInfo" /> interface for use by applications upgraded from Visual Basic 6.0.

Functions and objects in the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6> namespace are provided for use by the tools for upgrading from Visual Basic 6.0 to [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/includes/vbprvb-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 함수 및 개체가 <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6> 네임 스페이스를 Visual Basic 6.0에서의 업그레이드 도구에서 사용 하기 위해 제공 [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]합니다.

trans-unit.source: In most cases, these functions and objects duplicate functionality that you can find in other namespaces in the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 대부분의 경우에서 이러한 함수 및 개체에 다른 네임 스페이스에서 찾을 수 있는 기능이 중복 됩니다.는 [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)]합니다.

trans-unit.source: They are necessary only when the Visual Basic 6.0 code model differs significantly from the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] implementation.
trans-unit.target: 필요한 지만 때 Visual Basic 6.0 코드 모델이 크게 다릅니다에서 [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] 구현 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The number of <see langword="DBPROPIDSET" /> structures in <c>rgPropertyIDSets</c>.
An array of <see langword="DBPROPIDSET" /> structures.
A pointer to memory in which to return the number of <see langword="DBPROPSET" /> structures returned in <c>prgPropertySets</c>.
A pointer to memory in which to return an array of <see langword="DBPROPSET" /> structures.
Returns the current settings of all properties supported by the rowset.

trans-unit.source: The bookmark or chapter column for which to get the related rowset.
The IID of the interface pointer to return in <c>referencedRowset</c>.
A pointer to memory in which to return an <see langword="IUnknown" /> interface pointer on the rowset that interprets values from this column.
Returns an interface pointer to the rowset to which a bookmark or chapter applies.
